author: Thomas Franck
title: Goldman says one sign the pandemic may be getting better is fewer people Googling 'loss of smell'
description: "Data on the pace of virus spread are encouraging, suggesting that lockdowns have paid large dividends," Goldman's chief economist wrote.
content:
A woman wearing a face mask smells flower blossoms.
Goldman Sachs is optimistic that recent public safety measures to contain the spread of the coronavirus are working based on an unusual data source: Google searches for "loss of smell."
